{"tid":1753712,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"不滿門被鎖 日女一拳擊斃男友","createTime":"2019-11-25T04:11:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-25T04:41:07.000Z","uid":32511,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"d820e6291c7d623569d5a4be5a672c0f5c6ed39f","tid":1753712,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T04:11:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0UK8Wyv.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0UK8Wyv.jpg&h=5462bd01&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n日本埼玉縣一名22歲在餐飲店工作的女子，週五因為不滿同居男友鎖門，一拳朝他臉上揮擊，男子當場被擊斃，目前該女子已經警方逮捕。<br />\n <br />\n綜合日媒報導，案發在11日凌晨，日女山崎桃子外出買東西，回家後發現家門已被上鎖，就用拳頭打向21歲的男友木村昌史的臉部一下。事情過後，山崎還和木村一起睡覺，起床後，才發現男友一動也不動。山崎聯絡母親到場，母親到現場後立即報案，救護人員到達時發現木村已經死亡。<br />\n <br />\n報導也提到，警方將會進行大體解剖，確認山崎與木村死亡的關係。"},{"pid":"cddf15e18cd938145e7501a483827d30e1ec801b","tid":1753712,"uid":47775,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T04:13:04.000Z","msg":"到底係條女太強，定條仔弱<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"77c3ecdfbb8ce0a51d815b34e09cee2bdc5d8da6","tid":1753712,"uid":331173,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T04:13:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />一拳就死，咁克警咪打死好多人"},{"pid":"6972e554c84d7c9885a4b8634b54f3465c929d5b","tid":1753712,"uid":36383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T04:13:54.000Z","msg":"source?"},{"pid":"83ac5a672827077e561554fe5584c6226d4112fc","tid":1753712,"uid":255968,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T04:13:58.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"747f20d52894f7367e6775853ade8fa078ae9d57","tid":1753712,"uid":97330,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T04:14:13.000Z","msg":"S級英雄"},{"pid":"10408d2551eee0c4ba9941effe4106f2816d4ac0","tid":1753712,"uid":210059,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T04:14:30.000Z","msg":"我偶像<img src=\"/assets/faces/norma